This folder contains the bash-scripts to automatically build and install Linux from scratch version 7.9

Settings are contained in settings.script and should be reset to default values after install for security reasons.

To execute, run start.install script as root (using su in terminal is necessary)

Script tree:

+ start.install.script
  + install.script

    * LFS_SOURCES/install.script        # download sources

    + /tools/install.script		# set up toolchaine
      + /tools/install.withlfs.script
        + /tools/install.withbash.script

    + install.withchroot.script		# build lfs
      + install.withbash.script
        * install.withbash2.script
    * install.withchroot2.script
    * install.withchroot3.script
